OL,3,CSevern Trent Water ordered to pay
OL,4,C#600k after polluting brook with human
OL,5,Cwaste
OL,7,FSevern Trent Water is facing fines of
OL,8,Fmore than half a million pounds for
OL,9,Fpolluting a Leicester brook with human
OL,10,Fwaste.
OL,12,FThe Environment Agency's report found
OL,13,Fan "overwhelming" smell and visible
OL,14,Fhuman waste on a stretch of West
OL,15,FMeadow Brook at Whitwick, near
OL,16,FCoalville.
OL,18,FThe company admitted its fault and has
OL,19,Fnow agreed to pay money to a wildlife
OL,20,Forganisation as a penalty.
