OL,7,FNeil Ratcliffe, the investigating
OL,8,Fofficer for the East Midlands
OL,9,FEnvironment Agency, said: "Protecting
OL,10,Fthe environment in the East Midlands
OL,11,Fand taking action against those that
OL,12,Fdamage or threaten this is our utmost
OL,13,Fpriority.
OL,15,F"We will always consider prosecution
OL,16,Fin the most serious cases but
OL,17,FEnforcement Undertakings are an
OL,18,Feffective enforcement tool for less
OL,19,Fserious cases. They allow companies to
OL,20,Fput things right and contribute to
OL,21,Fenvironmental improvements.
