OL,7,F"They also allow polluters to correct
OL,8,Fand restore the harm caused to the
OL,9,Fenvironment and prevent repeat
OL,10,Fincidents by improving procedures."
OL,12,FThe agency said it was called to the
OL,13,Fbrook on September 12, 2022, and after
OL,14,Ffinding the discharged sewage had the
OL,15,Fflow stopped at Brooks Lane Pumping
OL,16,FStation the same day.
OL,18,FThe investigation revealed the
OL,19,Fdischarge had been on-going for some
OL,20,Fweeks before.
