OL,3,CSevern Trent Water ordered to pay
OL,4,C#600k after polluting brook with human
OL,5,Cwaste
OL,7,FSevern Trent said its staff had failed
OL,8,Fto see that pumps were not working
OL,9,Fproperly. Its teams had then failed to
OL,10,Fmonitor the site after the data-
OL,11,Fgathering system - which had allowed
OL,12,Fthem to do it remotely - had failed.
OL,14,FA Severn Trent spokesperson said: "We
OL,15,Faccept full responsibility for this
OL,16,Fincident and we hope that the
OL,17,Fcontribution to the Wildlife Trust
OL,18,Fwill hopefully go some way towards
OL,19,Fmaking this right.
